high_descs: Turn left, move to the counter where the head of lettuce is.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the apple into sections.
Turn right, move to the counter right of the dishwasher.
Place the knife on to the counter.
Turn left, move to the counter where the head of lettuce is.
Pick up a section of apple.
Turn right, move to in front of the stove.
Place the apple section into the microwave, cook it, pick it back up.
Turn right, move to the counter right of the dishwasher.
Place the apple section onto the counter, right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked section of apple onto the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the fridge.  Then turn right and walk to the counter just before reaching the door.  Turn to face the short edge of the counter near the door.
Pick up the knife that is on the right hand side of the apple on the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Holding the knife, turn right and walk to the fridge.  Then turn left and walk to the counter on the right hand side of the black dishwasher.
Put the knife down on the counter above and to the right of the dishwasher.
Turn around 180 degrees and walk to the fridge.  Then turn right and walk to the counter just before the door.  Turn to face the short edge of the counter near the door.
Pick up one piece of the apple on the counter.
Walk around the counter's edge you are currently facing, moving slightly to the right.  Continue walking along the counter to stand in front of the stove top.

Put the apple piece into the microwave that is above the stove top.  Put the apple piece on the right hand side of the egg.  Close the microwave door, microwave the apple for a few seconds, then open the door.  Take out the apple piece and close the microwave door.
Holding the apple piece, turn around 180 degrees.  Walk past the sink and stand in front of the counter to the right of the black dishwasher.
Place the apple piece onto the counter to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and heated apple piece onto a counter.

high_descs: Turn left, go straight to the fridge, turn right, go straight, turn right at the end of the counter and face the short end of the counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into pieces.
Turn right, go straight, turn left at the fridge, go straight to the counter to the right of the dishwasher.
Put the knife on the counter.
Turn around, go straight to the fridge, turn right, go straight, turn right at the end of the counter and face the short end of the counter.
Take a piece of apple from the counter.
Turn right, go past the counter then turn left, go straight, turn left at the oven.
Cook the apple in the microwave above the oven.
Turn around, go straight, turn left past the dishwasher, go to the counter to the right of the dishwasher.
Put the apple on the counter to the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple on a counter.

high_descs: Move to your left to the end of the counter by the head of lettuce.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Cut the apple into thirds.
Turn right towards the middle of the room and then move left to the dishwasher.
Set the knife on the counter above the dishwasher with the blade pointing towards the dishwasher.
Turn around and go back to the end of the counter with the head of lettuce.
Pick up one third of the apple.
Move forward to the microwave above the stove.
Cook the apple piece in the microwave for a few seconds and then take it out.
Turn around and move across the room to the dishwasher on your left.
Put the apple on the counter to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a piece of cooked apple on the counter with the knife.

high_descs: Move to stand at the end of the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the butter knife next to the apple.
Use the knife to slice the apple.
Carry the knife over to the counter where the dishwasher is.
Place the knife on the counter above the dishwasher.
Move back to the end of the counter where you sliced the apple.
Pick up a slice of apple from the counter.
Carry the apple slice to the stove.
Place the apple slice in the microwave above the stove, and then remove once heated.
Carry the apple slice to the counter by the dishwasher where you previously left the knife.
Place the apple on the counter to the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Move a heated slice of apple to the counter by the dishwasher.

high_descs: Go to the left side of the kitchen counter on the left.
Pick up the paring knife near the edge of the counter.
Cut the red apple into three parts.
Go to the kitchen counter  near the dish washer.
Place the paring knife on the counter top.
Turn around and go back to the left side of the kitchen counter on the left.
Pick up one piece of the cut apple.
Go to the microwave above the stove.
Microwave the apple next to the egg and take it out.
Turn around to go to the kitchen counter next to the dishwasher.
Place the apple on the right of the knife.
anns.task_desc: Microwave a cut piece of apple.
